{"tid":1561112,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★消費差？】主婦「Full Pay」買樓收租 認為社會事件得到解決，樓價會升","createTime":"2019-09-11T12:58:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-14T12:54:27.000Z","uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"768e67d03f5f6dfdde8a15c13cd1a73e6a7a56e6","tid":1561112,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T12:58:32.000Z","msg":"會德豐地產旗下的將軍澳日出康城9A期MARINI及9B期GRAND MARINI今日推售共318伙，吸引一眾投資客及自住買家。<br />\n<br />\n家庭主婦「Full Pay」買樓收租<br />\n<br />\n家庭主婦周太偕先生前來買樓，一炮過付約700萬元買入兩房單位，用作收租之用。她形容單位交通方便，開價吸引，即使市況波動亦無礙購買意欲。她未考慮近期社會事件的影響，認為會得到解決，「（樓價）會回落少少，但最後都會升。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3272832/org/eeb882446f491ef366ebfceda45024c0.jpg/BqQONSg4G9HC_2edEJQ0r3Y6S8S-e8pYYtgPE2LYDxM?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3272832%2Forg%2Feeb882446f491ef366ebfceda45024c0.jpg%2FBqQONSg4G9HC_2edEJQ0r3Y6S8S-e8pYYtgPE2LYDxM%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=7c126753&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/地產樓市/374253/marini兩期開售-周太full-pay-700萬購兩房-稱樓價最後都會升\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E5%9C%B0%E7%94%A2%E6%A8%93%E5%B8%82%2F374253%2Fmarini%E5%85%A9%E6%9C%9F%E9%96%8B%E5%94%AE-%E5%91%A8%E5%A4%AAfull-pay-700%E8%90%AC%E8%B3%BC%E5%85%A9%E6%88%BF-%E7%A8%B1%E6%A8%93%E5%83%B9%E6%9C%80%E5%BE%8C%E9%83%BD%E6%9C%83%E5%8D%87&d=y6uglPlKbSLkZz%2BcPL4okRTmJET03dBbukdTSFliYCA%3D&h=2ae0682c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/地產樓市/374253/marini兩期開售-周太full-pay-700萬購兩房-稱樓價最後都會升</a>"},{"pid":"4558a40bd2880a4f463cb0db9590530e445b78f3","tid":1561112,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T12:58:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkg